examples.en: He thought this was the easiest way to get rich.
It is easiest to break a chain at its weakest link.
The easiest and shortest of all deaths, beheading.
Hand washing is one of the easiest ways to help prevent the spread of nocuous germs.
He found it easiest to express himself in the language of poetry.
It's easiest to catch snakes early in the morning, while they're still cold and inactive.
